trans-unit.source: Defines an interface for invoking compilation of source code or a CodeDOM tree using a specific compiler.
trans-unit.target: Definerer et grensesnitt til å starte kompilering av kildekode eller en CodeDOM-tre ved hjelp av en bestemt kompilator.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > In the .NET Framework versions 1.0 and 1.1, code providers consist of implementations of <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeParser>, and ICodeCompiler.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE]> I .NET Framework-versjonene 1.0 og 1.1 kode leverandører som består av implementeringer av <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeParser>, og ICodeCompiler.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeParser> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: In the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnlong](~/add/includes/dnprdnlong-md.md)], the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.CreateGenerator%2A>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.CreateParser%2A>, and <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.CreateCompiler%2A> methods are obsolete, and the methods of <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator> and ICodeCompiler are directly available in the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> class.
trans-unit.target: I de [!INCLUDE[dnprdnlong](~/add/includes/dnprdnlong-md.md)], <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.CreateGenerator%2A>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.CreateParser%2A>, og <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.CreateCompiler%2A>metodene som er foreldet, og metoder for <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator>og ICodeCompiler finnes direkte i <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>klasse.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.CreateCompiler%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.CreateParser%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider.CreateGenerator%2A>

trans-unit.source: You should override those methods in your code provider implementation and not call the base methods.
trans-unit.target: Du må overstyre disse metodene i koden leverandøren implementeringen og ikke kall base-metoder.

trans-unit.source: The ICodeCompiler interface can be implemented for a specific compiler to enable developers to programmatically compile assemblies from Code Document Object Model (CodeDOM) compile units, strings containing source code, or source code files.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet ICodeCompiler kan implementeres for en bestemt kompilator slik at utviklere å kompilere programmatisk samlinger fra kode dokumentobjektmodellen (CodeDOM) kompilering enheter, strenger som inneholder kildekode og kildefiler i koden.

trans-unit.source: The ICodeCompiler interface provides the capability to invoke compilation with specified parameters at runtime and access information related to compilation after compilation occurs, including the result code, and any errors or warnings the compiler returns.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet ICodeCompiler gir muligheten til å aktivere kompilering med angitt parametere runtime og tilgang til informasjon relatert til kompilering etter kompilering oppstår, inkludert Resultatkode, og feil eller advarsler kompilatoren returnerer.

trans-unit.source: Each compile method accepts a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters> object that indicates settings for the compiler, and returns a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults> object that indicates the results of the compilation.
trans-unit.target: Hver kompilering metode godtar en <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters>objekt som angir innstillinger for kompilatoren, og returnerer et <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults>objekt som angir resultatene av kompileringen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters>

trans-unit.source: Compiler developers should provide an implementation of this interface to support dynamic compilation.
trans-unit.target: Kompilator utviklere må inneholde en implementering av dette grensesnittet for å støtte dynamisk kompilering.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementers should also consider implementing this interface to provide programmatic compilation capability for the language that they are providing CodeDom support for.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementerere bør også vurdere implementerer dette grensesnittet for å gi programmatisk kompilering funksjonen for språket som de tilbyr CodeDom støtte for.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>
